{"id": "1353303873409908858", "channel_id": "1353279786029420586", "author_id": "244028747999608832", "author_name": "vxvendetta", "content": "For some mechanics clarification you can look in this guide: \nhttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1305204021425995816\nIn general you can combine 2 realms, the difference between 2 mixed and one pure realm is that the pure realm get double the buffs for the Realm Mastery stat and some more stuff, but if you mix one realm whit Chaos you get all the effect of a pure realm plus some more buffs. \nYou can look of the effect of the stats and the mechanics of the realms on the guide or on the game if you go in the Team Lineup and click on the circle whit the selected realms.\nFor more guidance and guides I like to go in the fanserver in English, the link is in the Villa member bio, or I can send it, if you want.", "timestamp": "2025-03-23T09:46:26.591000+00:00", "thread_id": "1353279786029420586"}
